DocLocalization.Name: Hinzufügen / Addition von Teil zu Element - Relation

DocAttribute.Name: RelatingElement
DocAttribute.Documentation: Element at which a projection is created by the associated _IfcProjectionElement_.

DocAttribute.Name: RelatedFeatureElement
DocAttribute.Documentation: Reference to the _IfcFeatureElementAddition_ that defines an addition to the volume of the element, by using a Boolean addition operation. An example is a projection at the associated element.
